Class ComputusJunitTest

java.lang.Object
ComputusJunitTest
public class ComputusJunitTest
extends java.lang.Object
Junit test class to test method getEaster/Computus algorithm. Tests that the getEaster method is returning the correct Easter date for a given year. By extension is testing the Computus algorithm implemented in the Computus class constructor. Tests with known Easter dates from census.gov. Easter date source: link.
